Compressed Pcap Packet Indexing Program (CPPIP)
Mike Schiffman <mschiffm@cisco.com>
April 2013

=== Overview: =================================================================
CPPIP parses a bgzip (block-gzip) compressed pcap file and indexes packets for
subsequent extremely fast extraction.

Bgzip is described here:
http://blastedbio.blogspot.com/2011/11/bgzf-blocked-bigger-better-gzip.html
And available here:
http://sourceforge.net/projects/samtools/files/tabix/

A full write up of cppip including installation instructions and usage examples
can be found here: http://blogs.cisco.com/security/...
